---
import fs from 'fs'
import { join } from 'path'
import markdownToHtml from '../markdown'

const codeHTML = await markdownToHtml(fs.readFileSync(join(process.cwd(), 'router.txt'), 'utf8'))
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" name="viewport" />
    <title>Instantly secure your website with Security Headers and Edgio</title>
    <meta property="title" name="title" content="Instantly secure your website with Security Headers and Edgio" />
    <meta
      property="description"
      name="description"
      content="A demo that shows how to secure your website against some common attacks like XSS, code injection, clickjacking, etc."
    />
    <meta name="robots" content="max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1" />
    <meta name="og:url" property="og:url" content="https://rishi-raj-jain-security-headers-example-default.layer0-limelight.link" />
    <meta name="og:title" property="og:title" content="Instantly secure your website with Security Headers and Edgio" />
    <meta
      name="og:description"
      property="og:description"
      content="A demo that shows how to secure your website against some common attacks like XSS, code injection, clickjacking, etc."
    />
    <meta name="og:image" property="og:image" content="https://rishi-raj-jain-security-headers-example-default.layer0-limelight.link/cover.png" />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="en_IN" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:site" content="@rishi_raj_jain_" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Instantly secure your website with Security Headers and Edgio" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="A demo that shows how to secure your website against some common attacks like XSS, code injection, clickjacking, etc."
    />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://rishi-raj-jain-security-headers-example-default.layer0-limelight.link/cover.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:url" property="twitter:url" content="https://rishi-raj-jain-security-headers-example-default.layer0-limelight.link" />
  </head>
  <body class="flex w-full flex-col items-center">
    <div class="w-full md:max-w-2xl p-10 sm:p-0 flex flex-col items-center">
      <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-400">
        Instantly
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-pink-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">secure</span>
        your website with
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-pink-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Security Headers</span>
        and
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-pink-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Edgio</span>
      </h1>
      <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-medium text-gray-400">
        This is demo that shows how to secure your website against some common attacks like
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-pink-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          XSS, code injection, clickjacking, etc.
        </span>
        with
        <a
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://docs.edg.io?ref=rishi-raj-jain"
          class="border-b bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-pink-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >
          Edgio
        </a>
      </h2>
      <article class="mt-12 flex w-[90vw] flex-col items-center text-sm" set:html={codeHTML} />
      <h3 class="w-full text-left mt-8 text-3xl font-medium text-gray-600">Importance of Security & Headers</h3>
      <blockquote class="relative mt-8 flex flex-col">
        <svg
          width="16"
          height="16"
          fill="none"
          aria-hidden="true"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-16 w-16 -translate-x-6 -translate-y-8 transform text-gray-100 dark:text-gray-700"
        >
          <path
            d="M7.39762 10.3C7.39762 11.0733 7.14888 11.7 6.6514 12.18C6.15392 12.6333 5.52552 12.86 4.76621 12.86C3.84979 12.86 3.09047 12.5533 2.48825 11.94C1.91222 11.3266 1.62421 10.4467 1.62421 9.29999C1.62421 8.07332 1.96459 6.87332 2.64535 5.69999C3.35231 4.49999 4.33418 3.55332 5.59098 2.85999L6.4943 4.25999C5.81354 4.73999 5.26369 5.27332 4.84476 5.85999C4.45201 6.44666 4.19017 7.12666 4.05926 7.89999C4.29491 7.79332 4.56983 7.73999 4.88403 7.73999C5.61716 7.73999 6.21938 7.97999 6.69067 8.45999C7.16197 8.93999 7.39762 9.55333 7.39762 10.3ZM14.6242 10.3C14.6242 11.0733 14.3755 11.7 13.878 12.18C13.3805 12.6333 12.7521 12.86 11.9928 12.86C11.0764 12.86 10.3171 12.5533 9.71484 11.94C9.13881 11.3266 8.85079 10.4467 8.85079 9.29999C8.85079 8.07332 9.19117 6.87332 9.87194 5.69999C10.5789 4.49999 11.5608 3.55332 12.8176 2.85999L13.7209 4.25999C13.0401 4.73999 12.4903 5.27332 12.0713 5.85999C11.6786 6.44666 11.4168 7.12666 11.2858 7.89999C11.5215 7.79332 11.7964 7.73999 12.1106 7.73999C12.8437 7.73999 13.446 7.97999 13.9173 8.45999C14.3886 8.93999 14.6242 9.55333 14.6242 10.3Z"
            fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-800">
            As per <a class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/8405025" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"
              >HTTP security headers analysis of top one million websites</a
            >, "Globally, including both HTTP and HTTPS sites, CSP is implemented in 1.6% and CSP report only version in just 0.2% of sites."
          </p>
        </div>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg">
        Shocking! right? and the lack of CSP HTTP Header takes down the defense mechanisms against Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) and other client-side
        injection attacks
        <a class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samy_(computer_worm)" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"
          >which once took down MySpace.</a
        >
      </p>
      <p class="w-full mt-8 font-bold">
        Author: <a
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          href="https://rishi.app/about"
          class="border-b bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-pink-700 to-teal-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >
          Rishi Raj Jain
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="h-[50px]"></div>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dark.css" />
  </body>
</html>
